nodes.body_text:
Dear Komrades, we have good news!

Everyone can now update Yupitergrad to the 1.2 version and receive some quality of life improvements - i.a. UI tweaks, new leaderboard views (to check results of your Oculus Friends) and height adjustment.

Here’s the full list of things we added:
- New leaderboards where you can compare the results with your friends;
- Height adjustment option;
- Improved Time Attack UI which shows in real time if current result is better than your previous attempts;
- Improved menu - easier to find the most necessary options;
- Minor bug fixes.

Also, we want to thank you for your attention and such positive feedback! Our development team is really really moved by how you perceive the game. We can even reveal that some surprises are planned in the upcoming weeks!

We wish you all good health and stay safe!

Thank you,

Gamedust Team
